            "spec": "REAL HW (Receive): Block Adaptive Quantization — onboard lossy compression of the raw echo to save downlink bandwidth. Parameter: number of bits.\n\nSimulation: SKIPPED (full-precision complex64 kept). Placeholder; a future refinement could quantize s_raw to N bits/sample to study BAQ artifacts."
